N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 333.10 - Designation

State Regulations

The members of the academic staff of each college in
charge of the departments or divisions of such college shall be designated as
chairs of such departments or divisions, which designations shall be in
addition to their academic rank. Notes
